title: Transworld - And Now
description: Transworld Video #20. Transworld Skateboarding is proud to present our twentieth video, And Now. Starring six of skateboarding's rising young talents, this is the future of skateboarding now. And Now opens with David Gravette making heavy revisions to The Book Of Gnar. Matt Miller follows suit with more pop than a freshly stocked vending achine and ends his part with a speedy fakie hardflip noseblunt slide. Richie Jackson’s mind-expanding tricks fill his perception-altering part. Kenny Hoyle’s section is pure perfection.
